Dialogue: 9,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Oreki-san...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 9,0:11:49.39,0:11:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we assume your theory is correct, that would mean X-san is involved in something very bad...
Dialogue: 9,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it would.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:00.91,0:12:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 9,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,X is...
Dialogue: 9,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,involved in a crime.
