Dialogue: 9,0:12:20.42,0:12:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a game I'm playing with Chitanda.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:23.00,0:12:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I say doesn't necessarily have to be true.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:24.94,0:12:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, the whole point of this was to show that my theories can be completely off from reality.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:31.49,0:12:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what might this crime be?
Dialogue: 9,0:12:34.09,0:12:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:35.34,0:12:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's first assume that this theory is correct.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:38.46,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no police at this school, so there's a good chance that a related official is here.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:44.74,0:12:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming a crime took place, it must have happened on October 31st.
Dialogue: 9,0:12:49.91,0:12:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet the announcement was made today, just now, and seemingly in a hurry.
