Dialogue: 9,0:12:55.02,0:12:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take this to mean that the investigators only just now made that request.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:55.46,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95\t(0,100,\fscx95)\fscy100\t(0,100,\fscy100)\blur0.6\bord0\pos(344,289.71)\c&H191D1F&\b1}{left black below} Oct 31st{\b0}
Dialogue: 9,0:13:00.32,0:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they could also have made the request over the phone.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:03.79,0:13:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:05.57,0:13:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's safe to assume that the investigators would want to apprehend X.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, they'd need to come here in person.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apprehend...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:15.61,0:13:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So X-san was called on the premise that they're involved with the culprit somehow?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:19.83,0:13:21.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likely.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is just a game.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes, you're right...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:29.72,0:13:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't about the culprit, Shibazaki wouldn't have rushed with the announcement.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:35.62,0:13:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what crime did X commit?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:40.19,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 9,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 9,0:13:44.57,0:13:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoplifting comes to mind first.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps the crime was committed at a totally different place,
Dialogue: 9,0:13:49.46,0:13:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the investigators learned of someone fitting the culprit's description at Koubundou,
Dialogue: 9,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and based on that testimony, they came here to search.
Dialogue: 9,0:13:58.27,0:14:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, the crime could be anything.
